{"tid":1819013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"給已從美國amazon購買N95口罩或計劃從amazon購買N95口罩既人提示","createTime":"2020-01-10T11:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T07:22:07.000Z","uid":345571,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"026059de477f64b5f0093a2cf3e280f66ea48237","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"我有兩年美國網購經驗<br />\n監於武漢新冠狀病毒肺炎，現時N95同外科口罩抬價同缺貨。<br />\n如果你從美國amazon購買或計劃購買N95口罩，特別是1860(綠色版)<strong>同1870(獨立包裝版，千期不好買，</strong>我會在下面祥細解釋)醫用口罩，需要加倍注意。<br />\n首先，係amazon從第三方賣家或fulfilled by amazon購買，會有買到A貨同過期貨風險。至於賣家是amazon，都有可能買到退件、不符合形號物品甚至是用過貨品。可能是有消費者將用過啲貨調包，然後退貨俾amazon，人地打份工同處理啲貨非常多，基本上不可能逐件慢慢睇，除非好明顯，amazon係會將退件當新件賣。至於amazon有幾黑，你可以係google睇下或amazon評論區。<br />\n<br />\n3M Aura 1870口罩 同 3M Aura(9210 etc.)系列N95 口罩:<br />\n所有3M Aura N95 口罩沒有<strong>+</strong> (如1870+ ,9210+ etc)，<strong>千萬不要購買!!!</strong><br />\n無+符號都是舊版。以3M 1870 為例，從以下3M PDF 可以推測到好大可能最後一批3m 1870 生產時間大約2013 to 2014。N95口罩shelf life 是五年，即是好大可能市面上所有3M 1870 已經過期，有較小可能亞洲出產3M 1870 還未過期，歐洲出產3M 1870 基本上已過期。<br />\n<a href=\"https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/891340O/3m-aura-health-care-particulate-respirator-and-surgical-mask-1870-faq.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmultimedia.3m.com%2Fmws%2Fmedia%2F891340O%2F3m-aura-health-care-particulate-respirator-and-surgical-mask-1870-faq.pdf&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=a76e0282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/891340O/3m-aura-health-care-particulate-respirator-and-surgical-mask-1870-faq.pdf</a><br />\n或者向賣家查詢形號同過期時間(香港)，美國amazon 就不了，我已看過他們的手法，你問個啲fulfilled by amazon賣家，佢會話己入amazon 倉，不知道。<br />\n<br />\n3M 1860 綠色醫用版(3M 一直有生產這形號) amazon同eBay 好多好多and 好多過期貨<br />\n前面已説過fulfilled by amazon賣家不代表安全，一樣會有機會賣到A貨同過期貨。<br />\n青綠色盒3m 1860 兩個外國人一男一女個隻包裝and只有lot number，個啲3M 1860 係好大可能係過期貨同舊貨。<br />\n<br />\n基本上所有新版及新出產3M N95 均有used by date，如果你手上啲貨係只有lot number 同以上描述品相似and 有懷疑，請不好post上任何討論區，我見有人post 係連登，基於lot number係3M內部啲野，外人是無法得知同google 到，無人答到你，你都找不到，所以請你有禮貌地打3M 客務電話28071308，辦工時間星期一至星期五 8:30 to 17:30。或者到這個網站email: <a href=\"https://www.3m.com.hk/3M/zh_HK/company-hk/help-center/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.hk%2F3M%2Fzh_HK%2Fcompany-hk%2Fhelp-center%2F&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c690fea4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.hk/3M/zh_HK/company-hk/help-center/</a><br />\n我深信好多人從外地購買N95 mask including amazon，然後可能有大量人問3M 客服，啲客服就會變得不耐煩。<br />\n<br />\n所有N95 口罩and filter用個一次就要丟，不好嘗試用酒精，漂白水whatever消毒N95 口罩表面層，所有filter層一遇上液體，就失效。至於3M 1860 3M 1870+etc醫用口罩，有一層防水層，都不好嘗試消毒，本人對防水層測試過，除了能防水之外，其他液體如酒精，會破壞防水層同慘入filter層，不能使用。所有mask，filter軍用或民用都不具殺死(消毒)病毒，細菌，真菌等效能，只是阻住微生物。如果你曾經戴過既mask位置於高危地方如醫院，外地等，請用膠袋包好，然後放入有蓋垃圾桶。<br />\nGood luck"},{"pid":"e5763da2fbe147ac1e042b916ddb7f28c48bda6e","tid":1819013,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0aeb76e8daff228b06d713a356e6a2aa27682baf","tid":1819013,"uid":30615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打"},{"pid":"8b69b9e1116ebdfe3b34351c5f3d7fa1f33ec0cf","tid":1819013,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:54:18.000Z","msg":".push"},{"pid":"e2c15e76b413c5395613e422a0f525210466fea7","tid":1819013,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9b7945db72a2c8ab29cce2c78260e8d069bb76bc","tid":1819013,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"amazon 3m官方都唔得?"},{"pid":"57a6dfcde3b05db67db6303778e7e861dcaf13fb","tid":1819013,"uid":97552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"310648068fcc9d5d5c9b3668265b482407f4d3ea","tid":1819013,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"推 好重要"},{"pid":"94ac8db2eb6e3f880ebe52e15f718ca0992fb28b","tid":1819013,"uid":235892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"Amazon上面買左 3M 8511呢"},{"pid":"49c089ca5eeae633affa9fc7550389b86076cdbd","tid":1819013,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:16:16.000Z","msg":"piush"},{"pid":"6baea688715c261676c3562e8993c32468714c46","tid":1819013,"uid":303279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ac8db2eb6e3f880ebe52e15f718ca0992fb28b","tid":1819013,"uid":235892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"Amazon上面買左 3M 8511呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"0d16bbbb7c596c2c96d1830062e61f9b73a4d8a4","tid":1819013,"uid":211021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6baea688715c261676c3562e8993c32468714c46","tid":1819013,"uid":303279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ac8db2eb6e3f880ebe52e15f718ca0992fb28b","tid":1819013,"uid":235892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"Amazon上面買左 3M 8511呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"同問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"ed16a31ba832894e98e36b323b8072140eb09a82","tid":1819013,"uid":95937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:16:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea9bf84123f66d23ba2dac9cf892a7e787612595","tid":1819013,"uid":118553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:17:30.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fab2b52161965c7e7ecc1b420d3c59f002d9f0ef","tid":1819013,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"1870+唔係size?<br />\n之前做fit test都係1870+"},{"pid":"ea375692264fa063abd3f38d9e1cfbe1afb54ecb","tid":1819013,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"藥房都有係Amazon入貨，但藥房唔會理  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06287a92796fb648428d4ff9b8f773fdb76fecc","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b7945db72a2c8ab29cce2c78260e8d069bb76bc","tid":1819013,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"amazon 3m官方都唔得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"你要留意個賣家是不是amazon，由amazon官方出售比較有保障(但不是百分百，如我之前所說，有機會收到&quot;奇怪貨&quot;，睇你好不好彩。"},{"pid":"7a7edf65fcc0206750351d1f925c9150acd38934","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fab2b52161965c7e7ecc1b420d3c59f002d9f0ef","tid":1819013,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"1870+唔係size?<br />\n之前做fit test都係1870+"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:22:51.000Z","msg":"1870+係3M 最新aura 醫用版本，&quot;+&quot;並不是指size，&quot;+&quot;是改進意思(第二代)。1870無&quot;+&quot;係舊版本，基本上係已過期。3M 1870+ aura 只有一個size，並無s版本。"},{"pid":"6cd0cc5384435690bcea029ac84e26e1ddbdb241","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ac8db2eb6e3f880ebe52e15f718ca0992fb28b","tid":1819013,"uid":235892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"Amazon上面買左 3M 8511呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"3M 8511一直有生產，並無推出任何改進版，若果賣家是官方amazon，就應該大致上無問題，但都有小機會出事，如我之前所說，那就是amazon本身運作問題同不好彩。係買N95 Aura 版同 Aura 醫用版 1870+ (無+不好買)還有 N95 1860 就需要特別注意，我從來無見過amazon官方有出售這兩種版本口罩，全是由第三方售賣。"},{"pid":"ae85efc0f0504713778d95f989978872515df25f","tid":1819013,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"想問韓國製又有無分架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日上網買左哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GE2SFby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGE2SFby.jpg&h=9a088c91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e2f91fff811cb7eacfaca4b48affa8199045602","tid":1819013,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0f4eae45384b7d4490f449bf6b9fbac23a6c6269","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae85efc0f0504713778d95f989978872515df25f","tid":1819013,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"想問韓國製又有無分架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日上網買左哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GE2SFby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGE2SFby.jpg&h=9a088c91&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"KF94 是韓規，相等於N95。廠商不會做到盡剛剛好94，佢哋會留餘地，所以做 fit test + 正貨無過期，就可以發揮N95 相等效能，因為不是醫用版，所以應該係無防水層。"},{"pid":"1725669190493011fa0ad46bfd9680b9d73113c9","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"有興趣可以看這個N95的性能PDF(by 3M)<br />\n<a href=\"https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/409903O/respiratory-protection-against-biohazards.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmultimedia.3m.com%2Fmws%2Fmedia%2F409903O%2Frespiratory-protection-against-biohazards.pdf&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=f8b3d1e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/409903O/respiratory-protection-against-biohazards.pdf</a><br />\n還有P的防油性顆粒，並不是無限，是四十小時only。"},{"pid":"a16ced79a5f9d910b1cf756cc9fb68e9f2418653","tid":1819013,"uid":297577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f4eae45384b7d4490f449bf6b9fbac23a6c6269","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae85efc0f0504713778d95f989978872515df25f","tid":1819013,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"想問韓國製又有無分架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日上網買左哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GE2SFby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGE2SFby.jpg&h=9a088c91&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"KF94 是韓規，相等於N95。廠商不會做到盡剛剛好94，佢哋會留餘地，所以做 fit test + 正貨無過期，就可以發揮N95 相等效能，因為不是醫用版，所以應該係無防水層。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"其實有差別<br />\n<br />\nkf94係過濾94% 0.4微米<br />\nn95係過濾95% 0.3微米"},{"pid":"0a1c895649215c87227450d25c9415600c92ded7","tid":1819013,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a16ced79a5f9d910b1cf756cc9fb68e9f2418653","tid":1819013,"uid":297577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f4eae45384b7d4490f449bf6b9fbac23a6c6269","tid":1819013,"uid":345571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae85efc0f0504713778d95f989978872515df25f","tid":1819013,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"想問韓國製又有無分架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日上網買左哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GE2SFby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGE2SFby.jpg&h=9a088c91&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"KF94 是韓規，相等於N95。廠商不會做到盡剛剛好94，佢哋會留餘地，所以做 fit test + 正貨無過期，就可以發揮N95 相等效能，因為不是醫用版，所以應該係無防水層。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"其實有差別<br />\n<br />\nkf94係過濾94% 0.4微米<br />\nn95係過濾95% 0.3微米"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"明白，唔該曬"}]}